=\"UG_box_l\">\n    <!--微博实时热点-->\n    <h2 class=\"UG_box_title\">微博实时热点<\/h2>\n    <div class=\"UG_contents\">\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/dd853aafdc9eb7f8_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot01\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/dd853aafdc9eb7f8_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx1.sinaimg.cn\/large\/001MUaj1ly1gw4l26gr2lj60dw07tt9902.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/dd853aafdc9eb7f8_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#海底捞将关停300家左右门店#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#海底捞承诺妥善安顿关店员工#【#海底捞将关停300家左右门店#】11月5日消息，海底捞公告，本集团已决定在2021年12月31日前逐步关停300家左右客流量相对较低及经营业绩不如预期的海底捞门店（其中部份门店将暂时休整、择机重开，休整周期最长不超过两年）。本公司不会裁员并会于本集团内妥善安顿该等门 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/6e19844886e6bd4e_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot02\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/6e19844886e6bd4e_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx2.sinaimg.cn\/orj480\/0089OwKBly1gw4e92zhhvj31hc0u0q4m.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/6e19844886e6bd4e_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#抑郁症女子点外卖被聋哑骑手治愈#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【愿每个人都被温柔以待！#抑郁症女子点外卖被聋哑骑手治愈#】10月，江苏一名患有抑郁症的姑娘张迥在点奶茶时，遇到一位聋哑人骑手。当张迥看到这位骑手努力工作的样子后，内心突然涌上一股温暖，觉得自己被治愈了。记者联系到这位特殊骑手，他写到：“我每天跑12个小时，想多挣钱给儿子办婚礼”。 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c7bc632073846cb_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot03\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c7bc632073846cb_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/0033ImPzgy1gw4lytl3loj60ts1betkg02.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/8c7bc632073846cb_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#任何分裂祖国的行径解放军都将迎头痛击#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【国防部：台湾当局#任何分裂祖国的行径解放军都将迎头痛击#】5日，国防部新闻发言人吴谦就美方发表2021年《中国军事与安全发展报告》发表谈话。\n\n北京时间11月4日，美国国防部发布2021年《中国军事与安全发展报告》，报告罔顾事实、充斥偏见，妄议中国国防政策和军事战略，捏造所谓“中国军事威胁”， ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/2c52f5cba9e9ff1b_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/2c52f5cba9e9ff1b_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/pic8.iqiyipic.com\/image\/20211105\/9a\/9a\/v_163375709_m_601_480_360.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/2c52f5cba9e9ff1b_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#于和伟我睡七个小时怎么了#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#于和伟我睡七个小时怎么了# 看完《时间都去哪儿了》，@于和伟 会长说自己也是重度手机依赖患者，终于见到于会长在节目中“豪横”了一回，就是只睡七个小时怎么啦！#一年一度喜剧大赛#http:\/\/t.cn\/A6xwNOVF ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/a8cad8e957eddf36_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a8cad8e957eddf36_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/wx4.sinaimg.cn\/orj480\/005EifErly1gw4jiiz7azj31hc0u0jsp.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/a8cad8e957eddf36_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">#有个费钱的爱好是种什么体验#<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#2060# 这样满满当当一间房，能让手办爱好者一秒陷入疯狂！[打call]3D模型师、涂装师@CG张欢欢 外表看起来是个粗犷的猛男，内心却住着一个“柔软的胖子”～将喜欢的形象通过3D打印、涂装制作出来，最终呈现为一个完整的实体，给了他比单纯收集手办更大的成就感，也成就了他如今挚爱的事业！ ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\">a<\/i><\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n"})</script>
